title: DiRT.Rally.Hotfix.v1.0.109.3940-BAT
description:
DiRT Rally v1.0.109.3940 (c) Codemasters

Release Date: 12/07/2015        Protection: Steam

Cracked By..: BAT-TEAM          # of Files: few

Note:

New exe (v1.0.109.3361 vs v1.0.109.3940) pushed out a
few hours after final release. No idea what it fixes if
anything.

Game:

DiRT Rally captures the essence of what makes rally
unique  that sense of trying to remain in control, as
you hurtle along dangerous, undulating roads at
breakneck speed, aiming to squeeze everything out of
your car whilst knowing that one crash could irreparably
harm your stage time.

1. Unpack the release to where you installed the game.
2. Enjoy!
